data.title: Parkhurst Prison Warders A
data.text:
Records have been found between these dates, however, the person may have been on the Island longer. These will alter, if or when I find more. Birth records are their children. It may be that some of these officers from the date of 1912, worked at Camp Hill Prison, but unless the record said “Camp Hill”, I have included them in Parkhurst.

PARKHURST PRISON WARDERS A – F
